{"tid":708592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[終極贏家] 貿易戰反而讓「中日變盟友」！　外媒：兩國終於形成合作共識","createTime":"2018-06-19T12:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T01:27:49.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8cc2d2da994fe7cbc70cd20c0bc55d9d5ca791e","tid":708592,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:01:39.000Z","msg":"貿易戰反而讓「中日變盟友」！　外媒：兩國終於形成合作共識<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180619/1194220.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180619%2F1194220.htm&d=VK22I%2BFY%2FIjMh2OQidlJmtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bdd99143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180619/1194220.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美中貿易戰持續延燒，美國總統川普對中國採取強硬態度，不過《華爾街日報》指出，這反而讓中日成為貿易盟友，讓兩國終於形成合作共識。日本首相安倍晉三政府與北京當局在領土和安全問題上爭論多年後，開始主張和解，中日雙方近幾個月已停止交相指責。安倍月初時更表示，「我要將中日關係提升到嶄新的階段。」<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，此事不僅反映出川普的「美國優先」政策正在重塑國際關係，更凸顯出日本需要找到盟友，共同支撐二戰後自由貿易體系。<span style=\"color: red;\">上年度，日對中出口約1370億美元，多數為中國工廠生產要出口到美國的產品，包括iPhone等半導體和高科技電子產品。因此，川普對500億美元中國商品課徵25%關稅，最後可能波及日本。</span><br />\n<br />\n中日合作共識的形成有機可尋，李克強5月訪日是中國8年來首次有總理級領導人訪日，幾乎全程陪同的安倍形容，這是「向關係明顯改善邁出重要的第一步」。李克強在訪日期間幾乎沒有提及日本侵華歷史。他說，兩國應該向前看，日本作為出口大國與中國形成互補關係。而美國引發市場不安的各種舉措，也讓中國有機會塑造「渴望自由貿易的穩定可靠大國」形象。<br />\n<br />\n川普宣布將對中國總額500億美元進口商品課徵25%關稅後，18日又宣布，已經指示美國貿易代表，考慮將繼續對中國進口的商品加徵10%關稅，商品總價值大約2000億美元（約台幣6兆）。<span style=\"color: red;\">中國經濟成長趨緩，北京更期待日本在先進製程上的投資和技術。今年5月，習近平5月與安倍首次通電話時同意，目前是改善兩國關係的好時機。</span>"},{"pid":"f05e7f58460671d130727af266241fa9dcdb105f","tid":708592,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"外媒呢?"},{"pid":"4d444b968c95a2f02dcc5f6f775f4ed306d421ae","tid":708592,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f05e7f58460671d130727af266241fa9dcdb105f","tid":708592,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"外媒呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"華爾街日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9b1a44dbcfe5b89e5a6cb0ad00beac7c8969ab","tid":708592,"uid":22736,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"抗日神劇點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a6d99a325cfead00ef0b813b4c8a6263ead39d","tid":708592,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:10:13.000Z","msg":"WSJ 唔好跟太貼<br />\n幾舐共吓"},{"pid":"51840bbcd426b4524616cc61c15d7b0a546a0511","tid":708592,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/201222_554d99cd8892532b885192210377ca1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F201222_554d99cd8892532b885192210377ca1d.png&h=8f394bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/201226_c0e7bc883303646edfabf9e6aa42bf57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F201226_c0e7bc883303646edfabf9e6aa42bf57.png&h=eb52253c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87d44ffd1d80ccd1d6b141b0d31c6cf9c0c4ec1c","tid":708592,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4a6d99a325cfead00ef0b813b4c8a6263ead39d","tid":708592,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:10:13.000Z","msg":"WSJ 唔好跟太貼<br />\n幾舐共吓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb02af73dd893a6c453ea74832f95db3d673936","tid":708592,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:34